<dl id="n36219b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n36" href="#n36219b">N36 (VI.B.29)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n36all.htm#n36219b"> 219(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> now, I, <font color="green">[Moremon]</font> ~ <small>Orange</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n36219b"> <li>FW unlocated</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Mormonism.]</font> &hellip; and the Words of Mormon begins: &ldquo;And <mark>now, I, Mormon</mark>, being about to deliver up the record which I have been making, into the hands of my son, Moroni, behold I have witnessed almost all of the destruction of my people, the Nephites.&rdquo; <small> Charles W. Ferguson, <a name="CFCT" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CFCT"><cite title="source">The Confusion of Tongues</cite></a> (1928; rpt. May 1929) 372</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
